metrics_conclusion: Bassically has higher complexity than the average song  in terms Chord-Melody Tension.
key_conclusion: Bassically has sections analyzed in the following keys: B Dorian,  and B Minor.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: added D chord to end of measure 8

As much as it pains me to remove the syncopated chords, I must abide by the guidelines. I tied the chords together for legibility. I must prioritize making it easy to read and understand, over making the transcription playback sound cool. The song itself is what's supposed to sound cool!
